THEY WERE THE ONES THAT TAUGHT ME HOW TO FUNCTION LIKE A HUMAN.'.

THE MASTERMIND BEHIND ALL OF IT WAS DR. HAN VAN SPIEGELVICH. Sregluch He USED DNA SAMPLES FROM HIS TWO ASSISTANTS. THEY WERE SCIENTISTS AS WELL, BUT NOT AT SPIEGELVICH'S LEVEL. WASTHE ONLY SUCCESSFUL TEST SUBJECT.'.

Photo shared by Artistic Bros on August 23, 2021 tagging @boundlessthecomic. May be a cartoon of text that says 'IT MUST HAVE BEEN AROUND 10 YEARS AGO. WAS A NORMAL FOX THEN, GENETICALLY SPEAKING. THEY HELD THESE TESTS THE MIDDLE OF THE MOUNTAINS BECAUSE THEY WERE NOT LEGAL. NEVERTHELESS THEY DID NEERTHEESSD IT.'.

Photo shared by Artistic Bros on August 23, 2021 tagging @boundlessthecomic. May be an illustration of 1 person, standing and text that says 'mom DAC HIS TWO EMPLOYEES RAISED ME UNDER SPIEGELVICH'S STUDY. THEY SORT OF ADOPTED ME AND TOOK ME IN AS ONE OF THEIR OWN. WE BECAME CLOSE.'.
Photo shared by Artistic Bros on August 23, 2021 tagging @boundlessthecomic. May be an illustration of text.

Photo shared by Artistic Bros on August 23, 2021 tagging @boundlessthecomic. May be an illustration of standing and text that says 'SORRY TO SCARE YA. THIS ISMCAT ISMY CAT RUDY. OF COURSE. WAS ADVISED ABOUT YOUR SITUATION. EXTRA LEG ROOM SEATS ARE AT 9A AND 9B.'.

HIS DYING WISH WAS FOR MY PARENTS TO INTRODUCE ME TO THE WORLD. AN ARRANGEMENT WAS MADE AND ONLY SELECT CROWD WAS INVITED. MOST OF THEM WERE SCIENTIST, SOME WERE WORLD LEADERS. SHOWED MYSELF AS DIRECTED, AND IT BECAME AN UPROAR. THEY REACTED FEAR AS TO WHAT IMPACT COULD MAKE ON THE INTELLEGENCE LEVELS OF ALL SPECIES.'.

Photo shared by Artistic Bros on August 23, 2021 tagging @boundlessthecomic. May be a cartoon of text that says 'MY PARENTS HAD TO FLEE IMMEDIATELY AFTER. IT WASN'T LONG BEFORE THE GOVERNMENT DEEMED THE EXPIRIMENTS AS AN ACT OF TREASON. MY PARENTS SET ME UP IN THE MOUNTAINS, AND FOR MY SAFETY LEFT WITH NO TRACE OR TIE. THIS WAY COULDN'T BE FOUND. THE CLOSEST TRACE HAD WITH THEM WAS WHEN MET A FRIEND OF THEIRS 5 YEARS AGO. HE CHECKED IN ON ME. HIS NAME WAS HUGO. He LIVES IN INDIA. Pên'.

Photo shared by Artistic Bros on August 23, 2021 tagging @boundlessthecomic. May be an image of airplane and text that says 'So THAT'S WHY WE'RE GOING TO INDIA. TO FIND HUGO. MAYBE HE CAN LEAD US To MY PARENTS. KNOW YOU'VE BEEN FLEXIBLE IN JOINING ME ON THIS TRIP. BUT ΤΟ BE HONEST, WE'RE JUST GETTING STARTED.'.
